name: PuneTravellerGuide
0:
”Alexa, open Pune Traveller Guide”
”Alexa, Start Pune Traveller Guide”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pune traveller guide
des:
Hungry? Need a Bite or Crave for a crunch!? Ask Pune Traveller guide for Breakfast , lunch ,dinner or Coffee and Get one of the best recommended places for food .
Perhaps in a mood to travel and explore our beautiful city pune? Don't Worry This Skill will help you by recommending best spots for attractions for tourists !
For Hotel Recommendations simply invoke the skill and choose any option from 4 options to get the recommendation with a number to the hotel.
For Attractions ask the skill for recommending places.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
